remarks: The function values for a 1-1 function from a set with three different elements are different.  (Contributed by AV, 20-Mar-2019.)
statement:
f1dom3fv3dif.v $e |- ( ph -> ( A e. X /\ B e. Y /\ C e. Z ) ) $.
f1dom3fv3dif.n $e |- ( ph -> ( A =/= B /\ A =/= C /\ B =/= C ) ) $.
f1dom3fv3dif.f $e |- ( ph -> F : { A , B , C } -1-1-> R ) $.
f1dom3fv3dif $p |- ( ph -> ( ( F ` A ) =/= ( F ` B ) /\ ( F ` A ) =/= ( F ` C ) /\ ( F ` B ) =/= ( F ` C ) ) ) $.
